'''天主教薩拉特-坎帕納教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Zaratensis-Campanensis}}；{{lang-es|Diócesis de Zárate-Campana}}）是[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教梅塞德斯-路嫻總教區|梅塞德斯-路嫻總教區]]。<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 04.10.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/10/04/191004c.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-10-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191004125229/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/10/04/191004c.html |archivedate=2019-10-04 |language=en |date=2019-10-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

教區成立於1976年3月27日，位於[[布宜諾斯艾利斯省|布宜諾斯艾利斯省]]北部七縣。2004年有教友636,000人（佔轄區總人口90.9%）、卅二個堂區、八十七名司鐸。現任教區主教為{{link-es|伯多祿·瑪利亞·拉薩格|Pedro María Laxague}}<ref name="Vatican20151103">{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 03.11.2015 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2015/11/03/0852/01891.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-10-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129032131/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2015/11/03/0852/01891.html |archivedate=2019-11-29 |language=it |date=2015-11-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-de|辣法耳·義祿·雷|Rafael Eleuterio Rey}}和{{link-en|奧斯卡·薩林加|Oscar Sarlinga|奧斯卡·道明·薩林加}}<ref name="Vatican20151103" /><ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 03.02.2006 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2006/02/03/0060/00175.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-10-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191005044354/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2006/02/03/0060/00175.html |archivedate=2019-10-05 |language=it |date=2006-02-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

